Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沙沙宮選手的瓦倫登赫爾特直接命中了莉姆希選手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}她好像用護盾防下了煌式武裝的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}身體沒有受到損害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}難怪卡蜜拉主人會那麼戒備你呢沙沙宮紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的攻擊建立於完美的預測之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但也因此非常容易應對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}能感受到這種屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}也是因為主人賦予了我人格和心靈的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的話我銘記於心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我也全力迎戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼我出招了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什... 什麼莉姆希選手的秘密武器登場了嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}連那個無比膚淺的廢材都得到了防禦屏障這一面絕對之盾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼主人授予我相應的裝備也非常正常不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這把盧恩夏雷夫可以稱得上是絕對之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那就來比個高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}盧恩夏雷夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}四十一式煌型粒子雙炮瓦倫登赫爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}竟然抵消了嗎 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我才要說這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的劍技真是犀利得可怕啊 刀藤綺凜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}阿爾迪選手苦苦死守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}刀藤流的「連鶴」果真名不虛傳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的是毫無破綻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你應該也看出來了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}每次抵擋住你的劍技吾輩就會學習並不斷進化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你真是一位無比優秀的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}被他看見過的招式無法再奏效嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是像這樣完全陷入被動也缺乏了一些樂趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}儘管放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你可真亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}很可惜 吾輩的身體乃機械所鑄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你似乎沒有考慮到這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我的修行也還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}好了 獲得了那麼多優秀的資料 吾輩也得好好向你回禮才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}來吧 莉姆希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是時候展現那一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我不要你這低能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}為什麼現在要做那種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}再說了 使用那一招的決定權在於我 你沒有那個許可權
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}阿爾迪選手說的那一招究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而另一邊 沙沙宮選手從剛才開始好像幾乎沒有進行反擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}似乎需要時間來冷卻炮身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}盧恩夏雷夫的連射效能大約是瓦倫登赫爾特的 3 倍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但論破壞力還是我的更高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}爸爸打造的煌式武裝絕不會遜於卡蜜拉·帕蕾特的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以 接下來我要用事實來證明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}要用絕招了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}雖然我認為毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不過也罷我就陪你再比一次高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}盧恩夏雷夫 最大輸出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}PulI Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}咚咚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是千鈞一髮呀莉姆希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那個防禦屏障除了自己的周圍 在其它地方也能夠展開嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對... 對不起紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我沒能阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}不會綺凜你已經做得非常好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}話說回來...這麼一來我方就佔據優勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這可不見得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}阿爾迪雖然非我本願不過就聽你的吧
