Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}和我們聯手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}荒謬至極
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你這樣是不是太沒禮貌了呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這種事不是應該等到彼此熟識之後再開始的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}完全沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要你們提供協助 那我也會給你們相應的回報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}回報?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我已經準備好伴手禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你們看過之後再做判斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是芙羅拉打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真受不了她究竟去幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是尤莉絲·愛雷克西亞· 馮 · 裏斯妃特吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個終端的主人現在在我手裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}夭霧綾斗在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我就是芙羅拉她沒事吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}公主殿下天霧先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只是讓她昏過去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}只要你們答應我的要求我就會立刻放了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}什麼要求!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}立刻申請「黑爐魔劍」的緊急凍結處置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但如果你們通報警備隊或特務機關 或者放棄鳳凰星武祭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我就無法保證她的安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}克勞蒂雅 緊急凍結處置是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當使用者認為有危險的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就能夠提出申請強制封印純星煌式武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}當然封印是可以解除的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想綾斗應該再也無法使用「黑爐魔劍」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就是說一旦我這麼做了這傢伙就不會再原諒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那麼關於那項申請我具體要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真的沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}對不起 綾斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}但是這樣做了之後對方也不一定會放了芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}可是如果不這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}由我們來救出芙羅拉這樣就沒有任何問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}原來如此只要裝作接受要求的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}然後在此期間救出芙羅拉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想到了一個方案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我... 想要把芙羅拉的安全放在第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你的意思是你甘願放棄自己的願望?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沒關係為了保護重要的事物而選擇犧牲她那一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}抱歉我只顧著考慮自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你不用介意因為我的想法也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲我覺得你太害怕失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}有什麼辦法那種滋味嘗到一次就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}救出芙羅拉同時星武祭也要奪冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請你們抱持著這樣的氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我說這些不是站在學生會長的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}而是作為朋友給你們的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}克勞蒂雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我知道了全都按照犯人的要求去做也確實讓人很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}就採用克勞蒂雅的方案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}那我們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沙沙宮 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}尤莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}在朋友身陷困境之時挺身相助 這是理所當然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}你不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是的我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是嗎...也對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}紗夜綺凜拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}綾斗就請按照犯人的要求 去提出緊急凍結處置的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我會暗中打點進行拖延的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}因為這是星導館內部的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}外面的人絕不可能輕易得知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我想犯人之所以禁止你們放棄星武祭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}是為了便於確認綾鬥你是否接受了他的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}所以在確保芙羅拉安全之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請你把黑爐魔劍藏起來改用其它的煌式武裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}犯人的目標是綾斗和黑爐魔劍從這一點來看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}幕後黑手十有八九是狄路克·艾貝爾范
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這樣的話那實際行動的應該就是雷渥夫的諜報機關黑貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}搜查範圍可以集中在他們的大本營再開發區域那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}我這邊最多只能撐到明天十五點開始的閉幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}沙沙宮同學 刀藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}請你們趕在這之前救出芙羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看看能不能找到機會逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至少如果能跟公主殿下取得聯絡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}這個力量是「魔術師」?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}看來只能乖乖聽他的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\2c&HC08080&\3c&HC08000&\4c&HFFFF00&\b1\be1}至少目前這種狀況下

