Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\an8\2c&HC08000&\3c&HFF0000&\4c&H804000&\b1\be1}雨降り　木漏れ日　虹
